  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an acute, prospective, multi-center, non-randomized, investigational device exemption
      (IDE) clinical study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm the performance of new sensing circuitry, and to
      confirm the performance of a Ventricular Capture Management feature in subjects with
      implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD) leads connected to an external
      pacemaker/defibrillator.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
